            Modern Automation for ProPresenter
          </h1>

          <!-- Subheading -->
          <p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-balance text-lg text-muted-foreground animate-fade-in-blur delay-200">
            ProAssist brings AI and intelligent automation into your media workflow.
            Designed to work natively with ProPresenter and can also run as a standalone tool.
          </p>

          <!-- CTA Buttons -->
          <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 md:flex-row animate-fade-in-blur delay-500">
            <div class="bg-foreground/10 rounded-[calc(var(--radius-xl)+0.125rem)] border p-0.5">
              <a
                href="#download"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary px-5 py-2.5 text-base font-medium text-primary-foreground shadow transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90"
              >
                Download Free
              </a>
            </div>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/crownemmanuel/proassist"
              target="_blank"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl px-5 py-2.5 text-base font-medium text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-accent transition-colors"
            >
              View on GitHub
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Smart Verses Demo -->
      <div class="relative mt-8 overflow-hidden px-2 sm:mt-12 md:mt-20 animate-fade-in-blur delay-750">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 relative mx-auto max-w-5xl overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-zinc-700 p-6 shadow-lg shadow-zinc-950/25">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-emerald-500"></div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white text-center mb-6">Meet Smart Verses</h3>

          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-start">
            <!-- Demo Visual -->
            <div class="space-y-3 min-h-[420px]">
              <!-- Segment 1 -->
